'''High''' is a band from Calcutta, India. The band was formed in 1974 and officially disbanded in 1990 after Dilip, the main songwriter died. They have one album with Tolkien poems called the Tolkien Suite. They were heavily influenced by UK and USA pop and rock.
===Band Members===
*Dilip Balakrishnan was the singer-songwriter he played the guitar, keyboards, and blues harp. He had a untimely death at 39 years old in 1990 due to cancer which led to the band breaking up
*Lew Hilt    bass guitarist
*Nondon Bagchi    drummer
*Adi Irani    on lead guitar till 1975
*Subir Chatterjee    replaced Adi on lead guitar after Adi moved to Canada
